### Create a Booking
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-05-20",
  "startTime": "10:00:00",
  "endTime": "12:00:00"
}

### Try Overlapping Booking (Should Fail)
POST http://localhost:8080/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-05-20",
  "startTime": "11:00:00",
  "endTime": "13:00:00"
}

### Get All Bookings
GET http://localhost:8080/bookings

### Approve Booking (Change ID as needed)
PUT http://localhost:8080/bookings/1/approve
